@startuml Telemetry Ingestion Business Process
title Telemetry Ingestion Business Process

participant "IoT / Event\nProducer" as IoT
queue "Kafka\nCluster" as KF
participant "Telemetry\nMicroservice" as T
database "AWS RDS" as DB

IoT -> KF : Produce telemetry JSON\n(topic: AssetLinkID-UtilityOperator)

loop Continuous polling — for each subscribed topic
  KF -> T : Poll messages (kafka-clients)
  activate T
  T -> T : Deserialise JSON
  T -> T : Route by asset_type field\n(BATTERY / SOLAR / EV_CHARGER)
  T -> DB : INSERT time-series row (JDBC)
  DB --> T : OK
  T -> KF : Commit offset
  deactivate T
end

note over T, DB
  REST endpoint also available for other
  services to query stored telemetry.
  No Camunda orchestration — pure event-driven flow.
end note

@enduml
